title: S2 EP14: Dis-Lodged
description:
This week, Maggie and Tim talk about Season Two Episode Fourteen: Dis-Lodged. The episode where a member of a local brotherhood dies during an initiation ritual and Shawn + Gus enter to save the day yet again! Plus, we see a more sensitive side of Lassiter!
